name: title
Korotkova spaghetti CRCFT 9 wks: Kinematic of 9-week-old CRCFT mice handling spaghetti

name: description
Korotkova spaghetti CRCFT 9 wks: Original SIMI videos, DeepLabCut-tracked videos and csv files of body kinematics of 9-week-old hCdx2-FlpO;CR-Cre;R26-Ai65-LSL-FSF-tdTomato;Tau-LSL-FSF-DTR handling spaghetti. Control group. Individual trials for each mouse are recorded from 8 cameras and metadata for synchronization is stored as *.smp files.
